Description
-----------

The **red** keyword multiples the red channel of the associated map by the given value.

Usage
-----

    red <redval>

Parameters
----------

-   *redval* - the value by which the red channel of the image map should be multiplied

Example
-------

The following stage reduces the intensity of the red channel by half.

    {
       map path/to/image.tga
       red 0.5
    }

Notes
-----

Not Available.

